structures.vectors.interfaces

Interface IndexedDataStructure<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Generic type
    All Superinterfaces:
    DataStructure<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>, LinearDataStructure<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArrayList, ChainedIndexedDataStructure, DynamicallySizedArray, LinkedList

    public interface IndexedDataStructure<T>
extends LinearDataStructure<T>
    Abstract IndexedDataStructure structure. All vector-like structures (linear structures) will extend this abstract class
